title: Bug 121682: Exception throws when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description: Description: An exception is thrown when exporting data from the attached report.
OB: When trying to export the data from the table in the report, an exception occurs at the 'ReportEngineService.getMetaData()' function.
EB: Exporting the data from the table should be successful and should not result in any exception.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Add a table to the report that has a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row. 
2. Preview the attached report. 
3. Attempt to export the data from the table.
